post_upgrade() {
  cat <<END

Both the format and default filename for S3QL credential files
have changed. S3QL now uses an INI-style configuration format,
which is stored in ~/.s3ql/authinfo2 by default. See the section
entitled "Storing Authentication Information" in
/usr/share/doc/s3ql/rst/general.rst for more information.

END
}
